    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "The Frost Fair Yanyuedao is a +2 greater striking yanyuedao (use statistics for glaive) once wielded by a legendary military general from Goka. This weapon was constructed from pieces harvested from a dragon\u2019s body. When in an area of severe cold or colder, the Frost Fair Yanyuedao becomes a +3 major striking yanyuedao with a glowing blue cutting edge and the following ability.",
